des:
A joke is a display of humour in which words are used within a specific and well-defined narrative structure to make people laugh and is not meant to be taken seriously.It plays an important role in our understanding of ourselves, our society, and our world at large.It cools our tempers and warms our hearts.
so promote jokes and lead a happy life :)
